# Optional — enables the AI features:
#   • "Find signature fields with AI" (PDF field detection)
#   • "Extract signature with AI" (crop a signature out of a messy photo)
#
# Without any key, the app works fully; the AI buttons show a friendly
# "not enabled on this deployment" message and signing stays manual.
#
# The app prefers Gemini (free tier) and falls back to Anthropic/Claude.
# Set whichever you have — GEMINI_API_KEY takes priority if both are set.

# Recommended: free tier, no credit card. Get one at:
#   https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=

# Optional fallback. Requires API credits. Get one at:
#   https://console.anthropic.com/
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
